;
; Contract cell for the compact self-host bridge from dict/hashmap/red-black
; tree replacement payloads into live evidence. The current source runner can
; still lose late definitions after the full container stack, so the witness band
; performs the bridge matrix directly with already-live container predicates:
; `jcpr-safe?`, `jcrr-bytes`, and `jcrr-ready?`. This file names the model
; boundary without adding C/Rust or host calls.

